@page "/"
@inject NavigationManager Navigation
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.Authorization

<PageTitle>Fast Transport</PageTitle>

<header class="header">
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-brand">
            <a href="/">Fast Transport</a>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-nav">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/about-us">About Us</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/price-guide">Price Guide</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/gallery">Gallery</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/blog">Blog</a>
            <a class="nav-link" href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-contact">
            <span class="phone-number">+65 6775 3889</span>
            <span class="email-address">info@fasttransport.com</span>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-end">
            <button class="icon-button search-icon" @onclick="Search">
                <span class="oi oi-magnifying-glass" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </button>
            <NavLink class="nav-link" href="register">Register</NavLink>
            <NavLink class="nav-link" href="login">Login</NavLink>
            <button class="book-now">Book Now</button>
        </div>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="private-car-service">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>PRIVATE CAR SERVICE</h2>
        <p>
            In the last decade, private car services have revolutionized 
            urban transportation. Once dominated by traditional taxis and 
            public transit, the streets are now teeming with vehicles from
            companies like Uber and Lyft. These services offer a new level 
            of convenience and flexibility, but they also bring challenges
            and controversies.
        </p>
        <p>
            Private car services have a relatively short but dynamic history. 
            Initially, these services were similar to taxi services but with
            a personal touch. The advent of smartphones marked a turning point, 
            allowing companies to leverage technology for streamlined operations.
            Today, industry giants like Uber and Lyft have a global presence, 
            reshaping how people view personal transportation.
        </p>

        <p>
            The primary advantage of private car services is convenience. 
            With a few taps on a smartphone, users can summon a car to their 
            exact location and get real-time updates on its arrival. Safety 
            is another selling point; features like GPS tracking and driver 
            verification enhance passenger security. Economically, these services
            have created a flexible job market, allowing individuals to work as 
            independent contractors.
        </p>
        <p>
            Private car services have undeniably transformed urban travel, 
            offering unmatched convenience and reshaping economic opportunities. 
            However, they also pose challenges that need addressing, from regulatory
            compliance to environmental considerations. As society continues to evolve
            with technology, the role and impact of these services will be a critical
            area of discussion and development.
        </p>
        
        <img src="toyota.jpg" alt="Private Car Interior" />
    </div>
</section>

